BEGIN:VEVENT
DESCRIPTION:<a href="https://tfl.gov.uk/tube-dlr-overground/status/?Input=&lineIds=&dateTypeSelect=Future%20date&direction=&startDate=2026-08-02T03:30:00&endDate=2026-08-02T11:00:00">Disruption map.</a>\n\nLIONESS LINE: Sunday 2 August\, before 1200 and after 2030\, no service between Euston and Kilburn High Road. Use local buses or London Underground services via any reasonable route (entrance/exit at Euston\, Euston Square\, Kilburn Park and Queens Park stations). First through trains: Euston to Watford Junction 1215\; Watford Junction to Euston 1130. Last through trains: Watford Junction to Euston 2000\, Euston to Watford Junction 2045
